title: 820-00045 no post
message:
820-00045 here that apparently was freezing then went no post it has no liquid damage, it seems to have all power rails. But one thing throwing me off is that the SYS_DETECT LED is not lighting up, despite getting the correct power to it.

Anyone get any ideas?

title: 820-00045 no post
message: If it was freezing before dying then it is probably a cracked trace or bad RAM. The LED could just be bad. This board smells like rabbit hole...
